      "requiredLevel": 4,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Order-of-accuracy testing and method of manufactured solutions must be demonstrated for all governing equations.",
      "rationale": "Order-of-accuracy tests were performed for the flow solver but not for the hemolysis damage accumulation sub-model. Partial verification is insufficient at MRL 5."
