      "acceptanceCriteria": "Grid convergence index (GCI) must be computed for all QoIs with GCI < 5% on the fine grid.",
      "rationale": "GCI was computed for velocity and pressure fields; GCI for hemolysis index on the fine mesh is 8.3%, exceeding the 5% threshold. Discretization error is not fully controlled."
